  "metadata": {
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Adding a Glossary to a Playground Book"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can create a glossary for your playground book if its material introduces vocabulary",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that might be new to your audience.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Glossary entries appear in two places:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Tools (…) menu’s Glossary entry, which shows a list of all terms and descriptions.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Individual popovers for terms that you reference from within the prose of a playground",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "page.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Assemble-Terms-into-a-Glossary",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Assemble Terms into a Glossary",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Add a glossary by placing a property list containing the terms and definitions at",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the following path inside your playground book:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<book name>.playgroundbook/Contents/PrivateResources/Glossary.plist"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Xcode includes a property list editor you can use to create property lists.",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "For more information, see ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://help.apple.com/xcode/mac/current/#/dev3f399a2a6",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "in Xcode Help.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The top-level key in a glossary’s property list is a dictionary named ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Terms",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Inside",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that dictionary, nest a single dictionary for each term you want to define. The key",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for each nested dictionary is the name of the term you’re defining.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "adding-a-glossary-to-a-playground-book-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-Detail-Keys-to-a-Terms-Definition",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add Detail Keys to a Term’s Definition",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The dictionary you use to define a term has three parts. Each part requires a specifically",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "named key:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "text": "Required.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "strong"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " A string that defines the term. Definitions are displayed both in the full glossary and in the popovers that appear when the term is tapped in prose.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "code": "Definition",
                    "type": "codeVoice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "A dictionary you use to point to the first time a term is used in a book. This dictionary has two required keys: ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "code": "PageReference",
                        "type": "codeVoice"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": ", which is a link to the chapter and page where the term is first used; and ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "code": "Title",
                        "type": "codeVoice"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": ", which you use to name the link to the chapter and page.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Spaces and other special characters in ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "code": "PageReference",
                        "type": "codeVoice"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " must be encoded according",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "to the URI rules in ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-2",
                        "isActive": true,
                        "type": "reference"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": ". For",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "example, a reference to the “Commands” chapter’s “Issuing Commands” page is specified",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "by using the ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "code": "Commands/Issuing%20Commands",
                        "type": "codeVoice"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " URI.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "code": "FirstUse",
                    "type": "codeVoice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "A string you use to customize the term’s title. Use this key to localize terms. If you omit this key, the term is used as its own title.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "code": "Title",
                    "type": "codeVoice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "type": "termList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following image shows the parts of a glossary as they appear in Swift Playgrounds.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "adding-a-glossary-to-a-playground-book-2",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-Links-to-the-Terms-in-Your-Prose",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add Links to the Terms in Your Prose",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Link appropriately to your glossary terms throughout your playground book’s pages.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Link to a term on its first use, as well as any subsequent uses on later pages where",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you think learners might need to check the definition again.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use markup to add term links. An example of link markup for the term ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "command",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " is",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "[commands](glossary://command)",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Include this markup in the flow of the prose you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "write for the learning material in your playground book. The example below shows",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a term link in context.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "/*:",
            "In this challenge, you'll practice your [bug](glossary://bug)-finding skills by",
            "finding and rearranging the [commands](glossary://command) that are out of",
            "order in the code below.",
            "*/"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you tap the rendered link on a page, a popover appears with the definition of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the term.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "adding-a-glossary-to-a-playground-book-3",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
